substep.action:
Validate the path:
- Directory exists
- Contains a ticket file (ticket-YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md)
- Contains a research file (research-YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md)
- Contains a questions file (questions-YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md)
- Contains a worklog file (worklog-YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md)
- All files parse with valid YAML frontmatter

Store the bundle paths in session:
- {{session.ticket_path}}
- {{session.research_path}}
- {{session.questions_path}}
- {{session.worklog_path}}
- {{session.bundle_dir}}

If any file is missing or malformed, halt and report — the user must
re-run ticket-orient or fix the bundle.

substep.output:
Bundle loaded:
- Slug: {{session.slug}}
- Primary tag: {{session.primary_tag}}
- Status: {{session.ticket_status}}
- Owner: {{session.owner}}
- Glossary: {{session.glossary_summary}}
- Prior Q&A entries: {{count}}
- Linked DRs: {{count}} ({{aliases_if_any}})

Orient Summary present: yes

Entering Q↔R loop. First turn begins with current-state orientation.
